Entry.comment: General character bonuses: Bonuses applicable to any character (subject: CHARACTER_US or CHARACTER_THEM)
Add a relationship to a character, relating them to current LEADER_US
Remove a relationship from a character, that related them to current LEADER_US
Add a character to a council position, if unlocked, or remove them from one
Set a character to courtier, effecting resource yields and allowing jobs outside archetype (the four types have no direct mechanical difference)
City bonuses: Bonuses applicable to cities (SUBJECT_CITY)
Adds agent network to a CITY_THEM
Adds friendly or rebel units to random applicable tile in city
Adds resource to random applicable tile in city
Unit bonuses: Bonuses to apply to a unit (SUBJECT_UNIT)
Set sea unit promotions
Religion events: Bonuses to apply to a relegion subject (SUBJECT_RELIGION)
Non-player nation bonuses: Bonuses applied to nations other than the triggering one (subject: PLAYER_THEM)

For player declaring provoked war, and gaining legitimacy
Tribe bonuses: Bonuses applied to tribes (SUBJECT_TRIBE)

For player declaring arbitrary war on a tribe
For player declaring war on a tribe, and gaining legitimacy
